AGI - Forty workers victims of exploitation in agriculture (14 from Gambia, 4 from Senegal, 1 from Ghana, 3 from Macedonia, 3 from Tunisia, 1 from Pakistan, 1 from Nigeria, 1 from Guinea, 4 from Egypt, 2 from Albania, 3 from Morocco, 1 from Gabon, 2 from Bangladesh): for 30 of them, using the conditions, was asked and obtained the non-existence of the residence permit for serious occupational exploitation. The Carabinieri of the Nucleo Carabinieri Labour Inspectorate of Cuneo and the Provincial Commands of the Carabinieri of Cuneo and Bolzano, have carried out an order of interim precautionary measure of the temporary prohibition of exercising the professional or entrepreneurial activity - and another relative to the preventive seizure of 11 vehicles - issued from the gip of the Tribunal of Asti on request of the prosecutor of the Republic of the same center against 9 people (4 A part of the exploited workers has also been taken into account by O.I.M. 7 (International Organization for Migration) which has transferred them and incorporated them into SAI projects (Accoglience Integration System) in other Italian localities, far from Alba, the place of exploitation, for job inclusion in different entrepreneurial realities. Among these were also those who had found shelter in camps of fortune along the river Tanaro.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
<div </div
&nbsp;
The investigations, launched in April 2023 as a result of the activity 'inspective carried out by the Territorial Authority of Cuneo, ITL inspectors and with the contest of cultural mediators of the IIM (International Organization for Migration), has allowed to identify a widespread picture of labor exploitation throughout the area of Alba (CN) and neighboring territories (zone of the "Langhe") to a strong viticultural vocation, to damage of non-communicipal citizens. Rebuild by the military the network of exploitation: from a place of concentration of workers, the same were taken and transported by the corporals, holders of agricultural holdings of work account third parties, for use in conditions of exploitation in farms operating in the vineyards of the provinces of Cuneo, Asti and Alessandria.&nbsp;
